Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧透福尔摩斯没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本乡所读的小说里夹着便条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我誊了一份
